  "name": "RPlog_Crashlanding",
  "title": "Crashlanding!",
  "summary": "Aboard the shuttle Sanguine Raptor, the inexperienced Corellian girl Mira pilots toward Caspar while the nomadic Telgosse warrior Simon broods over his lost fingers and the smell of burning wires he cannot place. Neither of them actually knows how to land a ship, and as they bicker the vessel's hull overheats and plunges into an uncontrolled dive over Plaxton City. When Simon panics and seizes the co-pilot's controls, the shuttle goes into a barrel roll, clips the FLS tower shattering its windows, and tumbles out of control across the city. The Raptor finally crashes hard onto the roof of the Imperial Embassy, cratering the landing pad. Battered but miraculously unhurt, Mira and Simon take stock of their survival amid the wreckage, the ship now thoroughly destroyed.",
